    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Geometry | Dimension</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Why use &apos;Add Dimension&apos;? </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Use <text styleclass="T_Menu">Add Dimension</text><text style="font-style:italic;">&#32;</text>to add all Linear and Angular Dimensions:</para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">Length or a <text styleclass="Element">Line</text> or Radius or a <text styleclass="Element">Circle</text> or <text styleclass="Element">Arc</text><text styleclass="VariableName">. </text></li>
      <li styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Perpendicular Distance from a <text styleclass="Element">Line</text>, or <text styleclass="Interface">X-Axis</text>, or <text styleclass="Interface">Y-axis</text>, to a <text styleclass="Element">Point</text>&#32;</li>
      <li styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Angle between two <text styleclass="Element">Lines</text>, or the Angle from the <text styleclass="Interface">X-axis</text> or <text styleclass="Interface">Y-axis</text> to a <text styleclass="Element">Line</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Angle between three <text styleclass="Element">Points</text>.</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Geometry-Dimension" anchor="DimensionPoint">How to use add Dimensions</link></para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See also: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-Application-Settings" anchor="App-NumberFormat">Number-Format: Precision and Digits</link>, <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-Application-Settings" anchor="App-NumberFormat">Dimension Font Size</link></para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See also: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-Rename-Element">Rename</link><text styleclass="Body Text"> - helpful when you add </text><text styleclass="Interface">Dimensions</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> to a </text><text styleclass="Element">Design-Set</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
