                  <li styleclass="Body Text">Click the <text styleclass="Element">Point</text> then the <text styleclass="Element">Line</text> (note <text styleclass="Element">Arcs</text>, <text styleclass="Element">Circles</text> and <text styleclass="Element">Lines</text> have <text styleclass="Element">Points</text>)</li>
