          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Interface2">Method 2<text styleclass="VariableName">: Lock &amp; Specify in the Point Properties dialog box</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Interface2"><text styleclass="Notes">Note: </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">You can use </text>Method 2<text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> only if you have </text><text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">NOT</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> added to the </text><text styleclass="Element">Point </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">a dimension or a constraint.</text></para>
