          <para styleclass="VariableName">Angle between two Lines - Rules: </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The dimension shows next to your pointer when you select two <text styleclass="Element">Lines</text>. Before you click your mouse again to define the displayed angle, you can select which angle to display.</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">There are eight possible angle dimensions:</para>
          <list id="36" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
